Set the recommended tuned profile for your system.


Step.1) Install the tuned, start it and enable it
                 
yum install tuned -y
systemctl start tuned
systemctl enable tuned


Step.2) Check the available profiles
                
tuned-adm profile


Step.3) Check which profile is currently active.
                 
tuned-adm active


Step.4) Check which profile is recommended for us
                
tuned-adm recommend


Step.5) Set the virtual-guest profile.
                 
tuned-adm profile virtual-guest


